<p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>我国进入新的发展阶段，产业升级和经济结构调整不断加快，各行各业对技术技能人才的需求越来越紧迫，职业教育重要地位和作用越来越凸显。中国民办教育协会职业本科教育专业委员会成立仪式在江西软件大学井冈山校区成功举办，标志着职业本科教育发展进入了一个新的阶段。</strong></span><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689430822.png" alt="1746689430822.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689430822.png" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;">中国民办教育协会</p><p style="text-align: left;">职业本科教育专业委员会成立仪式</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689419462.png" alt="1746689419462.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689419462.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689408147.png" alt="1746689408147.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689408147.png" style=""><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689412726.png" alt="1746689412726.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689412726.png" style=""></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689397041.png" alt="1746689397041.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689397041.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;">揭牌仪式</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689378741.png" alt="1746689378741.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689378741.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;">聘书颁发仪式</p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689364902.png" alt="1746689364902.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689364902.png" style="width: 100%;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">中国民办教育协会职业本科教育专业委员会第一届理事会第一次会议在江西软件大学井冈山校区召开。专委会将致力于推动职业本科教育的高质量发展，为教育强国建设贡献力量。专委会的成立得到了各级领导和专家学者的大力支持，他们围绕本科职业教育的最新发展趋势和相关政策进行深入的交流研讨。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">中国民办教育协会职业本科教育专委会</span></p><p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">第一届理事会第一次会议</span><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689353202.png" alt="1746689353202.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689353202.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><br></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689327726.png" alt="1746689327726.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689327726.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689319862.png" alt="1746689319862.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689319862.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689311781.png" alt="1746689311781.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689311781.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689304277.png" alt="1746689304277.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689304277.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689299406.png" alt="1746689299406.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689299406.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689293976.png" alt="1746689293976.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689293976.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689288341.png" alt="1746689288341.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689288341.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689270742.png" alt="1746689270742.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689270742.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689263761.png" alt="1746689263761.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689263761.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689256502.png" alt="1746689256502.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689256502.png" style="width: 100%;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689243262.png" alt="1746689243262.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689243262.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689236823.png" alt="1746689236823.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689236823.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689226982.png" alt="1746689226982.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689226982.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689220262.png" alt="1746689220262.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689220262.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689213731.png" alt="1746689213731.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689213731.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p style="text-align: left;"><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689206266.png" alt="1746689206266.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689206266.png" style="width: 100%;"></p><p><img src="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689195701.png" alt="1746689195701.png" data-href="https://alumni.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1746689195701.png" style="width: 100%;"/></p>